01:18:24,483 --> 01:18:28,267
A requirement that the police must exhaust all alternatives before shooting.

1150
01:18:28,287 --> 01:18:30,189
A duty to intervene.

1151
01:18:30,310 --> 01:18:34,755
So if a police officer sees another police officer doing something wrong, they have a duty to intervene.

1152
01:18:35,425 --> 01:18:44,413
a ban at shooting at moving vehicles, requiring the police to do a use of force continuum, and finally, require comprehensive reporting from the police.

1153
01:18:44,833 --> 01:18:46,855
These are all things that should be on the books already.

1154
01:18:47,095 --> 01:18:48,996
I honestly don't know how many of them are on the books.

1155
01:18:49,056 --> 01:18:51,458
I believe that's why Chief Buckley's looking at that and he's gonna post about it.

1156
01:18:51,859 --> 01:18:53,480
We should pass all of these immediately.

1157
01:18:53,740 --> 01:18:55,262
There's no reason not to do any of them.

1158
01:18:55,302 --> 01:18:57,584
They'll make community policing stronger.

1159
01:18:58,224 --> 01:19:03,649
